flowRoot.flowPara: Selecting a password from the list opens a properties dialog. We could show some additional information here, if it's required.
Selecting a key from the list opens a properties dialog.
Details about keyrings aren't shown in the list.
One of your keyrings is locked. Unlock it to view the passwords it contains.
If there are locked keyrings, a dialog is shown to unlock them.
If keyring unlock is cancelled, a button is shown in the header bar.
Don't allow manually adding passwords: it doesn't make sense. Apps should add the passwords, and expose them here for editing/removal.
Try to avoid exposing too many implementation details, such as keyrings and certificates.
